          <element type="List" name="Personality Trait" requiredLevel="1" number="1" checksum="4c3beea5" isList="true" registered="2">I can find common ground between the fiercest enemies, empathizing with them and always working toward peace.</element>
          <element type="List" name="Personality Trait" requiredLevel="1" number="2" checksum="d532bf1f" isList="true" registered="3">I see omens in every event and action. The gods try to speak to us, we just need to listen</element>
          <element type="List" name="Ideal" requiredLevel="1" checksum="1089d3aa" isList="true" registered="2">Charity. I always try to help those in need, no matter what the personal cost. (Good)</element>
          <element type="List" name="Bond" requiredLevel="1" checksum="904c692a" isList="true" registered="3">I owe my life to the priest who took me in when my parents died.</element>
          <element type="List" name="Flaw" requiredLevel="1" checksum="2f3c616a" isList="true" registered="6">Once I pick a goal, I become obsessed with it to the detriment of everything else in my life.</element>
